snippet.title: EGYPTIAN BBQ! Trying EGYPTIAN STREET FOOD in Cairo Egypt
snippet.description:
I'm finally in #Cairo, #Egypt the land that's filled with unquestionable scientific thoughts that's I've been talking about on my Beyond Science channel. But I'm here to go on a #egyptian street food tour. 

Check out the tour I went on at:
https://belliesenroute.com/
